{"tid":1686151,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"「推爆1102終極文宣整合」三點維園->五點愛丁堡廣場人權及民主法案集會+五點遮打花園和你摺","createTime":"2019-11-01T03:07:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-02T00:01:05.000Z","uid":89882,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"ea399fa2d327be310f7a8fa71733fb45bafe5a36","tid":1686151,"uid":89882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T03:07:37.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">大家都知攬炒巴已經兩手準備定班恐怖分子唔會批維園流水式集會<br />\n唔講廢話，以下為聽日<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">最新</span></span>集會安排<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong>倒 數 最 後 <span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">28</span></span> 個鐘<br />\n希 望 大 家 盡 全 力 spread 開 聽 日 嘅 活 動 流 程</strong></span><br />\n※Airdrop(極重要)<span style=\"font-size: small;\">用下面呢張圖再加文宣去send成功率會大增</span><br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/24nSo75.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F24nSo75.jpg&h=5f6818b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</blockquote><br />\n※貼去各區街道，連儂牆<br />\n※派傳單(小心安全)<br />\n※FB(極重要) : 每個立場蘋果嘅post新即刻瘋狂放文宣圖，去大型嘅gp入邊開post放1102文宣<br />\n※Instagram <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">所 有 集 會 活 動 已 有 不 反 對 通 知 書</span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">請所有 和理非 一家大細 扶老攜幼 安心參與</span></div><br />\n</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/11/01/110311_fd967e4853b48923c5ac8977f2917a28.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F11%2F01%2F110311_fd967e4853b48923c5ac8977f2917a28.jpg&h=464c9753&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eHeNc33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeHeNc33.jpg&h=a8af2951&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/96HnMph.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.li